  "title": "ISic003236. Inscribed funerary urn of Flavianos",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\"><span data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φλαβιανός\">Φλαβιανὸς</span></span></span> · <span data-text=\"χρησ\n                    τὸς\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">χρησ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>τὸς</span> · <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">καὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἄμενπτος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ἄμεν(πτος)</span> · <span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ἔζη(σεν)</span> · <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span> · <span data-text=\"λζ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λζ\">λζ</span>´ · <span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">ῆ͡ν</span>(ας)</span> · <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>´ · <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέ(ρας)</span> · <span data-text=\"ι\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"ι\">ι</span>´ · </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φλαβιανός\">Φλαβιανὸς</span>  <span data-text=\"χρηστὸς\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">χρηστὸς</span>  <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">καὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἄμενπτος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ἄμενπτος</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"λζ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λζ\">λζ</span>  <span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνας</span>  <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρας</span>  <span data-text=\"ι\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"ι\">ι</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\"><span data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φλαβιανός\">ΦΛΑΒΙΑΝΟΣ</span></span></span>·<span data-text=\"χρησ\n                    τὸς\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">ΧΡΗΣ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΤΟΣ</span>·<span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"ἄμενπτος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ΑΜΕΝ</span>·<span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗ</span>·<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span>·<span data-text=\"λζ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λζ\">ΛΖ</span>·<span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">Μ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Η͡Ν</span></span>·<span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span>·<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕ</span>·<span data-text=\"ι\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"ι\">Ι</span>·</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Φλαβιανὸς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φλαβιανός\">ΦΛΑΒΙΑΝΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"χρηστὸς\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">ΧΡΗΣΤΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"ἄμενπτος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ΑΜΕΝΠΤΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"λζ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λζ\">ΛΖ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ι\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"ι\">Ι</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003236_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana (Photo by students of the Liceo Lazzaro)\" src=\"ISic003236_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003236.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana (Photo by students of the Liceo Lazzaro)\" src=\"ISic003236-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy (Prag)</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Phlabianos (Flavianus), worthy and blameless, lived for 37 years, 3 months, 10 days.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">Serena Agodi</p>  <p>Flaviano, degno e innocente, visse 37 anni, 3 mesi, 10 giorni.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>According to Paolo Orsi, the urn still contained the deceased’s ashes when it was discovered, and traces of gilding were still visible on some of the letters and the capital of one of the relief columns. The use of the name Flavianus suggests a date after the beginning of the Flavian dynasty (beginning with Vespasian, 69 AD), but Flavianus’ status as slave, freedman, or free remains uncertain. The use of architectural elements in the form of the chest and a tabula ansata to frame the inscription are typical features of ash chests of this period.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi NSA 1915 216 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Libertini 1937 50 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001867\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001867</a>  </li><li> Wilson 1990 134 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 87 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Neat and regular square letters. Phi and omicron are rhomboid in form; standard four-bar sigma; epsilon has horizontal bars of equal length; alpha has a slightly extended apex; mu has extended apices, and all four strokes are full length and off-vertical. There is one instance of ligature in line 3, and interpuncts are in the form of simple triangular incisions.</p> Line 1-4  15-20  Not measured    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
